As a general hospital with spacious and superior infrastructure in the Ben Cat area with investment from owner Becamex, My Phuoc General Hospital has an important position because it is located in an area adjacent to many industrial parks. The major industry of Ben Cat Town, where people and hundreds of thousands of workers live and work, need to be examined and treated every day further than the areas of Bau Bang, Chon Thanh, Binh Long, Binh Long. Phuoc also focuses on medical examination and treatment here due to the closer distance to Saigon, in addition to the treatment of a number of experienced older doctors who have worked at large hospitals in Saigon for many years. Patients praise it, but unfortunately, with a young team of doctors and nurses, the process of medical examination and treatment is still limited, and the medical equipment and machinery are not up to par so the treatment can really be done. The accuracy is not yet complete, so more or less patients and family members who visit the patient directly complain, and since the inauguration of the new infrastructure, we have noticed that fewer and fewer people come for medical examination and treatment. Private hospitals near newly opened industrial parks such as: Nhan Nghia clinic (My Phuoc 2), Hoang Hao (My Phuoc 3) further away is Van Phuc (VSIP 2), however if daily limitations are not overcome My Phuoc hospital's leading position will no longer exist, which is a pity.
